com.m3rcuriel.controve.control.statespace

Class StateFeedbackPlant

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.m3rcuriel.controve.control.statespace.StateFeedbackPlant

  • public class StateFeedbackPlant
extends java.lang.Object
    A representation using DoubleMatrix of the plant in State Feedback. This class should be used mainly in simulation to check a plants reponse to a controller.
